@startuml
title SearchRec Overall Architecture
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "BusinessSystem" as BusinessSystem
rectangle "app_searchrec.views\n(SearchRec*View)" as SearchRecAPI
rectangle "SearchRecService\n(search / recommend / rank)" as SearchRecService

package "Adapters" as adapters {
  rectangle "IndexAdapter" as IndexAdapter
  rectangle "VectorAdapter" as VectorAdapter
  rectangle "FeatureStoreAdapter" as FeatureAdapter
  rectangle "EmbeddingProvider\n(SimpleTextEmbeddingProvider)" as EmbedProvider
}

package "Backends" as backends {
  rectangle "MemoryIndex" as MemoryIndex
  rectangle "OpenSearch" as OpenSearch
  rectangle "MemoryVector" as MemoryVector
  rectangle "Qdrant" as Qdrant
  rectangle "Milvus" as Milvus
  rectangle "MemoryFeatureStore" as MemoryFeature
  rectangle "FeastOnlineStore" as Feast
}

BusinessSystem --> SearchRecAPI : HTTP API
SearchRecAPI --> SearchRecService

SearchRecService --> IndexAdapter : search, upsert,\nget_document
SearchRecService --> VectorAdapter : search, upsert
SearchRecService --> FeatureAdapter : upsert,\nget_doc_features,\nget_user_features

note bottom of SearchRecService
  **Fusion scoring** (lexical + vector + tags + popularity + score_boost)
  is implemented inside **SearchRecService.search**.
  **rank** recomputes **final_score** from caller-supplied
  base_score / ctr_score / freshness_score only — **no adapter I/O**.
end note

VectorAdapter ..> EmbedProvider : <<optional>>\nQdrantVectorAdapter only\n(encode query & documents)

IndexAdapter --> MemoryIndex
IndexAdapter --> OpenSearch
VectorAdapter --> MemoryVector
VectorAdapter --> Qdrant
VectorAdapter --> Milvus
FeatureAdapter --> MemoryFeature
FeatureAdapter --> Feast
@enduml
